high_descs: Stand up turn around walk towards the dining table.
Pick up the pencil from the dining table.
Turn around walk towards the counter top.
Keep the pencil on the top of the counter top.
anns.task_desc: Pick up the pencil from the dining table and keep it on the counter top.

high_descs: Turn left and go straight, turn left towards the dining table
Pick up pencil from the dining table
Turn around and go straight, turn right towards the countertop
Put the pencil in the counter top
anns.task_desc: Placing the pencil in the counter top

high_descs: Go straight towards the wall and then walk straight into the room, turning to the dining table on your right.
Pick up pencil from the desk.
Head straight towards the counter top by turning around and turning left.
Place pencil on the counter top.
anns.task_desc: Changing pencil from one place to another.
